{
  "name": "Net Master",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/equipment.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You take no penalties for using a net that has not been folded and apply any enhancement bonus to attack rolls that the net possesses to all your Strength checks against a creature entangled by the net, and to the DC of Strength checks to burst your nets. You add half your base attack bonus to the escape artist DC to escape your nets.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you may make drag and reposition attempts against creatures entangled by your nets as long as you control the trailing rope. You may add any enhancement bonus to attack rolls that the net possesses on these combat maneuver checks. This talent applies to any weapon that functions as a net, such as the lasso (as applicable) and snag net.</p>\n",
